snippet.title: Off-Road Paradise: Trial 4x4 - Launch Trailer [VR, HTC Vive, Oculus Rift]
snippet.description:
Launch trailer for Off-Road Paradise: Trial 4x4, a realistic virtual reality off-road experience. Developed by Ivanovich Games, available for HTC Vive and Oculus Rift. You can find more information, as well as reviews and ratings here: https://vrgamecritic.com/game/off-road-paradise-trial-4x4
